quests.desc: I hope you're ready to go into rooms and interact with objects, because you've just entered TextWorld! Here is your task for today. First off, attempt to head north. After that, travel north. After that, make an attempt to move east. Next, make an effort to travel south. Then, move east. Okay, and then, try to move east. Then, head south. With that over with, try to head south. With that over with, take a trip west. Next, recover the cd from the couch. Alright, thanks!

objective: Who's got a virtual machine and is about to play through an exciting round of TextWorld? You do! Here is how to play! First off, go to the north. Then, make an effort to travel north. Following that, travel east. And then, try to venture south. With that accomplished, try to move east. Then, take a trip east. Okay, and then, go south. After that, make an effort to go to the south. After that, try to venture west. After that, retrieve the cd from the couch. And if you do that, you're the winner!

main_quest.desc: Who's got a virtual machine and is about to play through an exciting round of TextWorld? You do! Here is how to play! First off, go to the north. Then, make an effort to travel north. Following that, travel east. And then, try to venture south. With that accomplished, try to move east. Then, take a trip east. Okay, and then, go south. After that, make an effort to go to the south. After that, try to venture west. After that, retrieve the cd from the couch. And if you do that, you're the winner!
